[KANNADA] Ranadheera | 1988 |  x264 | AAC | Webrip | Phantom

Ranadheera is a 1988 Kannada language blockbuster musical action film starring V. Ravichandran and Kushboo in the lead roles. Directed by Ravichandran himself, the film was produced by his father N. Veeraswamy under Eshwari Productions. Kushboo gained popularity in South India through this film. The music was composed by Hamsalekha.

The film was a remake of Hindi superhit film &quot;Hero&quot; directed by Subhash Ghai.

All songs and lyrics were composed by Hamsalekha. The soundtrack was hugely successful upon release:
&quot;Ba Baaro Baaro&quot; - S. P. Balasubramanyam, Chorus
&quot;Ba Baaro Baaro&quot; (Bit) - Chorus
&quot;Baaramma Praanave&quot; - S. P. Balasubramanyam
&quot;En Hudgiro&quot; - Vani Jayaram, S. P. Balasubramanyam
&quot;Meenakshi Ninna Kanna&quot; - S. P. Balasubramanyam
&quot;Naavindu Haado&quot; - S. Janaki, S. P. Balasubramanyam
&quot;Ondanondu Kaaladalli&quot; - P. Susheela, Ramesh
&quot;Preethi Maadabaaradu&quot; - S. Janaki, S. P. Balasubramanyam
